      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "一个神经网络刚出生时，权重是随机的，几乎什么都不会。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "它却能通过看大量例子，一点点学会识别图像、翻译语言。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "让它学会的核心算法，就是今天的主角：反向传播。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "forward",
      "line_id": "fwd-1",
      "filename": "forward-fwd-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/forward-fwd-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.76,
      "size": 44208,
      "text": "先看前向传播。输入从左边进来，逐层加权求和再经激活函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "forward",
      "line_id": "fwd-2",
      "filename": "forward-fwd-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/forward-fwd-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "信号一路向右流动，最后在输出层得到网络的预测值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "forward",
      "line_id": "fwd-3",
      "filename": "forward-fwd-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/forward-fwd-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "这里我们用一个小小的二二一网络，来学习异或这样的模式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "loss",
      "line_id": "loss-1",
      "filename": "loss-loss-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/loss-loss-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "预测出来了，可它对不对呢？我们用损失函数来衡量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "loss",
      "line_id": "loss-2",
      "filename": "loss-loss-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/loss-loss-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "损失就是预测值和真实目标之间差距的平方，越小说明学得越好。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "loss",
      "line_id": "loss-3",
      "filename": "loss-loss-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/loss-loss-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "训练的目标，就是想办法把这个损失一步步降到最低。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "backward",
      "line_id": "back-1",
      "filename": "backward-back-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/backward-back-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "关键问题是：每个权重该往哪个方向、调多少，才能减小损失？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "backward",
      "line_id": "back-2",
      "filename": "backward-back-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/backward-back-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "答案是求损失对每个权重的偏导数，也就是梯度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "backward",
      "line_id": "back-3",
      "filename": "backward-back-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/backward-back-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "用链式法则，把输出端的误差沿着连线一层层反向乘回去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "backward",
      "line_id": "back-4",
      "filename": "backward-back-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/backward-back-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "于是误差从右向左流动，每条连线都算出自己那份梯度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "点单步训练，观察红蓝箭头标出的梯度，权重沿负梯度更新一次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "再看下方的损失曲线，随着一次次迭代，它稳稳地向下走。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "前向传播算出预测，损失衡量它离目标有多远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "反向传播用链式法则求出梯度，梯度下降据此更新权重。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "backpropagation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/backpropagation/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "这一前一后的循环，就是深度学习的引擎，我们下次再见！"
    }
